channel.title: Why the hell is NetBanes the only damn thing thats slow on my comp?
channel.description: I defragged my computer, deleted old files. Cleaned it out all to get NetBeans to run like it was yesterday. It wont. Netbeans laggs.. When i open a window and close it netbeans goes grey and you have to move your mouse around to reveal the buttons again. The last thing i downloaded was the windows vista transformation pack.
